# Preserve exact bytes on every platform so the canonical tree round-trips
# losslessly into ~/.claude. The source tree is LF except where noted below.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Legacy CRLF source files: preserved as CRLF on checkout so the round-trip is
# byte-identical to the current ~/.claude original (else Gate 2 diff != 0).
assets/claude/README.md text eol=crlf
